findings.title: Owner can change tax and liquidity fees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify tax and liquidity fees.

findings.title: Owner can change maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount.

findings.title: Owner can include/exclude from maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to include or exclude certain addresses from the maximum transaction amount, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses or users from paying fees.

findings.title: Owner can change minimum number of tokens to add to liquidity
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the minimum number of tokens required to add to liquidity.

findings.title: Owner can change charity, utility, development and donation address
findings.description: The owner has privileges to change charity, utility, development, and donation addresses.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw contract BNBs
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw contract BNBs.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has privileges to lock and unlock, which could allow them to retake ownership even after renouncing it.
